# Weather Forecast Dashboard 🌦

## Description
A modern, responsive weather dashboard built with HTML, Tailwind CSS, and JavaScript. It allows users to search for weather conditions by city or use their current location.

## Features
- 🌍 Search by city
- 📍 Use current location
- 📆 5-day forecast
- 📊 Today's highlights (humidity, pressure, wind, visibility)
- 💡 Dark theme UI
- 📱 Responsive design

## Tech Stack
- HTML5
- Tailwind CSS
- JavaScript
- OpenWeatherMap API

